Facilitates loading of a json file with well attributes.

The file needs to follow the format below. The categorical attributes     are completely flexible.
{
    "version" : "0.1",
    "wells" : [
        {
            "alias" : {
                "eclipse" : "OP_1"
            },
            "attributes" : {
                "mlt_singlebranch" : "mlt",
                "structure" : "East",
                "welltype" : "producer"
            },
            "name" : "OP_1"
        },
        {
            "alias" : {
                "eclipse" : "GI_1"
            },
            "attributes" : {
                "mlt_singlebranch" : "singlebranch",
                "structure" : "West",
                "welltype" : "gas injector"
            },
            "name" : "GI_1"
        },
    ]
}

